== 評價 ==
在[[IGN|IGN]]的「前25名哈利波特人物」中小仙女·東施名列第25位<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/06/26/top-25-harry-potter-characters|title=Top 25 Harry Potter Characters|accessdate=2018-07-14|date=2017-06-26|last=Staff|first=I. G. N.|work=IGN|language=en-US|archive-date=2017-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171108173001/http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/06/26/top-25-harry-potter-characters|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]》選出的25名最偉大的《哈利波特》人物中，小仙女·東施名列第22位<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/greatest-harry-potter-characters/|title=The 25 Greatest Harry Potter Characters|accessdate=2018-07-14|date=2011-07-26|publisher=Empire|language=en|archive-date=2018-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180801122239/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/greatest-harry-potter-characters/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

